              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " smolagents' CodeAgent lets the LLM generate Python code that calls tools \u2014 enabling composable multi-step computation with loops and arithmetic. ToolCallingAgent is the traditional JSON tool-call alternative for models that support it. Pydantic AI pairs the tool-calling loop with strict type safety: agents return validated Pydantic models, tools receive typed dependencies via RunContext, and validation failures trigger automatic LLM retries. Use smolagents for flexible tool composition with Hugging Face models; use Pydantic AI for type-safe production agents that integrate naturally with FastAPI."
